<arggraph id="micro_k022" topic_id="allow_shops_to_open_on_holidays_and_sundays" stance="con">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[It is quite clear that Sunday should remain a day of rest.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[For you can go shopping 6 days a week,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[as shops are open till 10pm on some days.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Thus Sundays should remain a day for getting together with family,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[otherwise there will be a new kind of leisure activity where people spend their time in supermarkets instead of outside or in conversation etc.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[Furthermore, there's no need to keep shops open on Sundays.]]></edu>
